data.description:
Seller is motivated to sell.
Two spacious living areas. Galley kitchen with tile backsplash opens to dining area & family
room. Stained concrete throughout common areas. Oversized master bedroom with walk-in closet. Large backyard for
entertaining! Deck with pergola, fire pit area, & stone pavers create additional patio space.
Home is extremely well maintained. Foundation repaired with transferable warranty, Roof is about 6 yrs old and the HVAC system is about 1 yr old. Feeds to Kennedale schools! Walking distance to elementary school and no HOA
